{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm a savant,"},{"time":2000,"text":"or more precisely,"},{"time":4000,"text":"a high-functioning"},{"time":6000,"text":"autistic savant."},{"time":8000,"text":"It's a rare condition."},{"time":10000,"text":"And rarer still when accompanied,"},{"time":13000,"text":"as in my case,"},{"time":15000,"text":"by self-awareness"},{"time":17000,"text":"and a mastery of language."},{"time":20000,"text":"Very often when I meet someone"},{"time":23000,"text":"and they learn this about me,"},{"time":25000,"text":"there's a certain kind of awkwardness."},{"time":28000,"text":"I can see it in their eyes."},{"time":31000,"text":"They want to ask me something."},{"time":34000,"text":"And in the end, quite often,"},{"time":36000,"text":"the urge is stronger than they are"},{"time":39000,"text":"and they blurt it out:"},{"time":41000,"text":"\"If I give you my date of birth,"},{"time":43000,"text":"can you tell me what day of the week I was born on?\""},{"time":45000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":48000,"text":"Or they mention cube roots"},{"time":51000,"text":"or ask me to recite a long number or long text."},{"time":55000,"text":"I hope you'll forgive me"},{"time":57000,"text":"if I don't perform"},{"time":60000,"text":"a kind of one-man savant show for you today."},{"time":64000,"text":"I'm going to talk instead"},{"time":67000,"text":"about something"},{"time":69000,"text":"far more interesting"},{"time":71000,"text":"than dates of birth or cube roots --"},{"time":74000,"text":"a little deeper"},{"time":76000,"text":"and a lot closer, to my mind, than work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"I want to talk to you briefly"},{"time":81000,"text":"about perception."},{"time":84000,"text":"When he was writing the plays and the short stories"},{"time":87000,"text":"that would make his name,"},{"time":89000,"text":"Anton Chekhov kept a notebook"},{"time":92000,"text":"in which he noted down"},{"time":94000,"text":"his observations"},{"time":96000,"text":"of the world around him --"},{"time":98000,"text":"little details"},{"time":100000,"text":"that other people seem to miss."},{"time":103000,"text":"Every time I read Chekhov"},{"time":106000,"text":"and his unique vision of human life,"},{"time":110000,"text":"I'm reminded of why I too"},{"time":112000,"text":"became a writer."},{"time":114000,"text":"In my books,"},{"time":116000,"text":"I explore the nature of perception"},{"time":118000,"text":"and how different kinds of perceiving"},{"time":121000,"text":"create different kinds of knowing"},{"time":123000,"text":"and understanding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"Here are three questions"},{"time":130000,"text":"drawn from my work."},{"time":132000,"text":"Rather than try to figure them out,"},{"time":134000,"text":"I'm going to ask you to consider for a moment"},{"time":137000,"text":"the intuitions"},{"time":139000,"text":"and the gut instincts"},{"time":141000,"text":"that are going through your head and your heart"},{"time":143000,"text":"as you look at them."},{"time":146000,"text":"For example, the calculation:"},{"time":149000,"text":"can you feel where on the number line"},{"time":151000,"text":"the solution is likely to fall?"},{"time":154000,"text":"Or look at the foreign word and the sounds:"},{"time":157000,"text":"can you get a sense of the range of meanings"},{"time":159000,"text":"that it's pointing you towards?"},{"time":162000,"text":"And in terms of the line of poetry,"},{"time":165000,"text":"why does the poet use the word hare"},{"time":167000,"text":"rather than rabbit?"},{"time":171000,"text":"I'm asking you to do this"},{"time":173000,"text":"because I believe our personal perceptions, you see,"},{"time":177000,"text":"are at the heart"},{"time":179000,"text":"of how we acquire knowledge."},{"time":181000,"text":"Aesthetic judgments,"},{"time":183000,"text":"rather than abstract reasoning,"},{"time":186000,"text":"guide and shape the process"},{"time":188000,"text":"by which we all come to know"},{"time":191000,"text":"what we know."},{"time":193000,"text":"I'm an extreme example of this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"My worlds of words and numbers"},{"time":199000,"text":"blur with color, emotion"},{"time":201000,"text":"and personality."},{"time":203000,"text":"As Juan said,"},{"time":205000,"text":"it's the condition that scientists call synesthesia,"},{"time":208000,"text":"an unusual cross-talk"},{"time":210000,"text":"between the senses."},{"time":216000,"text":"Here are the numbers one to 12"},{"time":218000,"text":"as I see them --"},{"time":220000,"text":"every number with its own shape and character."},{"time":224000,"text":"One is a flash of white light."},{"time":226000,"text":"Six is a tiny and very sad black hole."},{"time":231000,"text":"The sketches are in black and white here,"},{"time":234000,"text":"but in my mind they have colors."},{"time":236000,"text":"Three is green."},{"time":238000,"text":"Four is blue."},{"time":240000,"text":"Five is yellow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"I paint as well."},{"time":247000,"text":"And here is one of my paintings."},{"time":250000,"text":"It's a multiplication of two prime numbers."},{"time":254000,"text":"Three-dimensional shapes"},{"time":256000,"text":"and the space they create in the middle"},{"time":259000,"text":"creates a new shape,"},{"time":261000,"text":"the answer to the sum."},{"time":264000,"text":"What about bigger numbers?"},{"time":266000,"text":"Well you can't get much bigger than Pi,"},{"time":270000,"text":"the mathematical constant."},{"time":272000,"text":"It's an infinite number --"},{"time":274000,"text":"literally goes on forever."},{"time":276000,"text":"In this painting that I made"},{"time":278000,"text":"of the first 20 decimals of Pi,"},{"time":282000,"text":"I take the colors"},{"time":284000,"text":"and the emotions and the textures"},{"time":287000,"text":"and I pull them all together"},{"time":289000,"text":"into a kind of rolling numerical landscape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294000,"text":"But it's not only numbers that I see in colors."},{"time":297000,"text":"Words too, for me,"},{"time":299000,"text":"have colors and emotions"},{"time":301000,"text":"and textures."},{"time":303000,"text":"And this is an opening phrase"},{"time":305000,"text":"from the novel \"Lolita.\""},{"time":307000,"text":"And Nabokov was himself synesthetic."},{"time":311000,"text":"And you can see here"},{"time":313000,"text":"how my perception of the sound L"},{"time":316000,"text":"helps the alliteration"},{"time":318000,"text":"to jump right out."},{"time":321000,"text":"Another example:"},{"time":323000,"text":"a little bit more mathematical."},{"time":325000,"text":"And I wonder if some of you will notice"},{"time":327000,"text":"the construction of the sentence"},{"time":329000,"text":"from \"The Great Gatsby.\""},{"time":333000,"text":"There is a procession of syllables --"},{"time":336000,"text":"wheat, one;"},{"time":338000,"text":"prairies, two;"},{"time":340000,"text":"lost Swede towns, three --"},{"time":343000,"text":"one, two, three."},{"time":345000,"text":"And this effect is very pleasant on the mind,"},{"time":349000,"text":"and it helps the sentence"},{"time":351000,"text":"to feel right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"Let's go back to the questions"},{"time":356000,"text":"I posed you a moment ago."},{"time":359000,"text":"64 multiplied by 75."},{"time":362000,"text":"If some of you play chess,"},{"time":365000,"text":"you'll know that 64"},{"time":367000,"text":"is a square number,"},{"time":370000,"text":"and that's why chessboards,"},{"time":372000,"text":"eight by eight,"},{"time":374000,"text":"have 64 squares."},{"time":377000,"text":"So that gives us a form"},{"time":379000,"text":"that we can picture, that we can perceive."},{"time":382000,"text":"What about 75?"},{"time":385000,"text":"Well if 100,"},{"time":387000,"text":"if we think of 100 as being like a square,"},{"time":390000,"text":"75 would look like this."},{"time":393000,"text":"So what we need to do now"},{"time":395000,"text":"is put those two pictures"},{"time":397000,"text":"together in our mind --"},{"time":399000,"text":"something like this."},{"time":402000,"text":"64 becomes 6,400."},{"time":406000,"text":"And in the right-hand corner,"},{"time":410000,"text":"you don't have to calculate anything."},{"time":412000,"text":"Four across, four up and down --"},{"time":414000,"text":"it's 16."},{"time":417000,"text":"So what the sum is actually asking you to do"},{"time":419000,"text":"is 16,"},{"time":421000,"text":"16, 16."},{"time":424000,"text":"That's a lot easier"},{"time":426000,"text":"than the way that the school taught you to do math, I'm sure."},{"time":429000,"text":"It's 16, 16, 16, 48,"},{"time":431000,"text":"4,800 --"},{"time":433000,"text":"4,800,"},{"time":435000,"text":"the answer to the sum."},{"time":438000,"text":"Easy when you know how."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":443000,"text":"The second question was an Icelandic word."},{"time":446000,"text":"I'm assuming there are not many people here"},{"time":449000,"text":"who speak Icelandic."},{"time":451000,"text":"So let me narrow the choices down to two."},{"time":456000,"text":"Hnugginn:"},{"time":458000,"text":"is it a happy word,"},{"time":460000,"text":"or a sad word?"},{"time":462000,"text":"What do you say?"},{"time":465000,"text":"Okay."},{"time":467000,"text":"Some people say it's happy."},{"time":469000,"text":"Most people, a majority of people,"},{"time":471000,"text":"say sad."},{"time":473000,"text":"And it actually means sad."},{"time":477000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":480000,"text":"Why do, statistically,"},{"time":483000,"text":"a majority of people"},{"time":485000,"text":"say that a word is sad, in this case,"},{"time":487000,"text":"heavy in other cases?"},{"time":490000,"text":"In my theory, language evolves in such a way"},{"time":493000,"text":"that sounds match,"},{"time":495000,"text":"correspond with, the subjective,"},{"time":498000,"text":"with the personal,"},{"time":500000,"text":"intuitive experience"},{"time":502000,"text":"of the listener."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505000,"text":"Let's have a look at the third question."},{"time":509000,"text":"It's a line from a poem by John Keats."},{"time":512000,"text":"Words, like numbers,"},{"time":515000,"text":"express fundamental relationships"},{"time":518000,"text":"between objects"},{"time":520000,"text":"and events and forces"},{"time":522000,"text":"that constitute our world."},{"time":524000,"text":"It stands to reason that we, existing in this world,"},{"time":527000,"text":"should in the course of our lives"},{"time":529000,"text":"absorb intuitively those relationships."},{"time":532000,"text":"And poets, like other artists,"},{"time":535000,"text":"play with those intuitive understandings."},{"time":538000,"text":"In the case of hare,"},{"time":541000,"text":"it's an ambiguous sound in English."},{"time":543000,"text":"It can also mean the fibers that grow from a head."},{"time":546000,"text":"And if we think of that --"},{"time":548000,"text":"let me put the picture up --"},{"time":550000,"text":"the fibers represent vulnerability."},{"time":554000,"text":"They yield to the slightest movement"},{"time":557000,"text":"or motion or emotion."},{"time":560000,"text":"So what you have is an atmosphere"},{"time":564000,"text":"of vulnerability and tension."},{"time":566000,"text":"The hare itself, the animal --"},{"time":568000,"text":"not a cat, not a dog, a hare --"},{"time":571000,"text":"why a hare?"},{"time":573000,"text":"Because think of the picture --"},{"time":575000,"text":"not the word, the picture."},{"time":577000,"text":"The overlong ears,"},{"time":579000,"text":"the overlarge feet,"},{"time":581000,"text":"helps us to picture, to feel intuitively,"},{"time":584000,"text":"what it means to limp"},{"time":587000,"text":"and to tremble."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"So in these few minutes,"},{"time":592000,"text":"I hope I've been able to share"},{"time":594000,"text":"a little bit of my vision of things"},{"time":597000,"text":"and to show you"},{"time":600000,"text":"that words can have colors and emotions,"},{"time":603000,"text":"numbers, shapes and personalities."},{"time":606000,"text":"The world is richer,"},{"time":608000,"text":"vaster"},{"time":610000,"text":"than it too often seems to be."},{"time":613000,"text":"I hope that I've given you the desire"},{"time":616000,"text":"to learn to see the world with new eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}